    "description": "Your homeworld is under siege!, upgrade your ship, modify your weapons and fight your way through sectors now controlled by the enemy for a last chance to survive and counterattack.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Strike</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Fight over 18 unique enemies and 3 different bosses on your way to<br>the final level where a massive battle awaits you.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2239470/extras/e3edea14136b2adba6a90c027771520e.poster.avif?t=1692465187\" width=482 height=272 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2239470/extras/e3edea14136b2adba6a90c027771520e.webm?t=1692465187\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2239470/extras/e3edea14136b2adba6a90c027771520e.mp4?t=1692465187\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Branching map</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Plot your course on a branching map with different rewards and challenges.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2239470/extras/ce830391a969cdaf32e57da563fa3fc4.poster.avif?t=1692465187\" width=482 height=280 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2239470/extras/ce830391a969cdaf32e57da563fa3fc4.webm?t=1692465187\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2239470/extras/ce830391a969cdaf32e57da563fa3fc4.mp4?t=1692465187\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Choose your ship</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>There are 6 ship variants with different stats and abilities to choose from<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2239470/extras/47899f78bff3ab29ccf0cd7259d4e1ea.poster.avif?t=1692465187\" width=482 height=280 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2239470/extras/47899f78bff3ab29ccf0cd7259d4e1ea.webm?t=1692465187\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2239470/extras/47899f78bff3ab29ccf0cd7259d4e1ea.mp4?t=1692465187\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Upgrade</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Upgrade your weapons and modify their stats to fight your own way<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2239470/extras/619aaa1ee89f7beacd17a9f7d9e5ea0b.poster.avif?t=1692465187\" width=482 height=272 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2239470/extras/619aaa1ee89f7beacd17a9f7d9e5ea0b.webm?t=1692465187\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2239470/extras/619aaa1ee89f7beacd17a9f7d9e5ea0b.mp4?t=1692465187\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Rescue</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Allied ships across different sectors are also under attack, help them <br>to increase your chances of winning<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2239470/extras/c6cff5c2c1ee111b24695ca387b42805.poster.avif?t=1692465187\" width=482 height=272 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2239470/extras/c6cff5c2c1ee111b24695ca387b42805.webm?t=1692465187\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2239470/extras/c6cff5c2c1ee111b24695ca387b42805.mp4?t=1692465187\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Maneuver</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Some enemies won't be easy to destroy, use your piloting skills to <br>outmaneuver them<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2239470/extras/dbb6153aafd3c50a52b7a397c4cd2133.poster.avif?t=1692465187\" width=480 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2239470/extras/dbb6153aafd3c50a52b7a397c4cd2133.webm?t=1692465187\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2239470/extras/dbb6153aafd3c50a52b7a397c4cd2133.mp4?t=1692465187\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >2 different movement systems</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Choose between arcade and simulator modes to customize your gameplay <br>experience and challenge yourself.</li></ul><br><strong>Other features:</strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Ship upgrades<br></li><li>Randomized levels<br></li><li>Dynamic music<br></li><li>Random events<br></li><li>Interactive environment<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2239470/extras/0d9e12c863cfb82923f53ffad461beb3.poster.avif?t=1692465187\" width=482 height=272 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2239470/extras/0d9e12c863cfb82923f53ffad461beb3.webm?t=1692465187\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2239470/extras/0d9e12c863cfb82923f53ffad461beb3.mp4?t=1692465187\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></li></ul>",
